## Post-Onboarding Checklist

After the onboarding session, confirm:

- [ ] Tenant created with correct province, timezone, subscription tier
- [ ] API key generated and shared securely (shown once, never stored in plain text)
- [ ] At least one sender profile configured with all contact methods
- [ ] DMS contacts imported — verify imported count against source CSV
- [ ] Express consent records added for any customers with documented opt-ins
- [ ] First compliance audit generated — note the baseline score
- [ ] Compliance program document generated
- [ ] Dashboard account created for the compliance officer
- [ ] Dealership understands: pre-send checks, consent expiry alerts, unsubscribe handling
- [ ] Next touchpoint scheduled (1-week check-in)

