## Common Onboarding Issues

| Issue | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `full_name is required` on import | Using first_name/last_name instead of full_name | Combine into single full_name field |
| Express consent not created | Missing express_purpose in import payload | Record separately via POST /api-consent with all required fields |
| `qualifying_event is required` on consent API | Missing the free-text qualifying_event description | Add qualifying_event (description), qualifying_event_type (enum), and qualifying_event_date |
| Low consent coverage score | Many contacts with no purchase/inquiry dates in DMS | Normal for first import — run re-consent campaign for no_consent contacts |
| Sender profile incomplete warning | Missing phone, email, or website_url | Update the profile to include all three contact methods |

